_sText:
This is my remade version of the original deathrun_temple from Counter-Strike 1.6 by XPaw and also my second finished map so far, feel free to leave some feedback!

Original map: https://gamebanana.com/maps/142244

The map got a total of 15 traps
8 Death spawns
32 Runner spawns
Attempted ambient sound

I made the map to be on my deathrun server but I'd like to share it with people on gamebanana aswell, I hope you like it! If you have Garry's mod and would like to try it on the deathrun gamemode you can join the StarCrew deathrun

Enjoy! :')
